author: ritchiem
msg: QPID-1764 : Update to BaseTransactionLog to create a TestableTransactionLog, which will replace TestableMessageStore. Update to BaseTransactionLog/Test to work correctly with transactions and to fully test that functionality. Updated StoreContext to know when it is in a transaction as relying on a payload being set is not sufficient as that is not set when running with the MessageMemoryStore and so transactional testing in the BTLT was not correct.
Update to Virtualhost to correctly set the RoutingTable when the specified TransactionLog is wrapped in a BaseTransactionLog.

author: ritchiem
msg: QPID-1778 : Increased delay as tcp testing takes longer than inVm. Now checks failover doesn't occur and we know about it in less time than the connectiondelay which would be waited for if we attempted failover.
